title: 2014 - The Year In Christian Music (Bundle 75)
description:
-----------------------------------------------------------------------
2014 - THE YEAR IN CHRISTIAN MUSIC
-----------------------------------------------------------------------

This is my final bundle for 2014.  I reached my share goal of 2400 titles this year.  That surpasses the 1669 titles we shared back in 2013, the 1461 we shared in 2012, and the 964 that got these bundles all started in 2011.

Time permitting, I might be able to put together a few discographies for the rest of 2014.  But I also plan on doing plenty of traveling, so IÃ¢â‚¬â„¢m not sure how much free time, if any, that I will have over the next month or so.
